## Executive Overview

The AFAT-X10V2 FULL DEPLOYMENT ARCHITECTURE represents the **complete activation and system-wide embedding** of the AFAT aerodynamic intelligence layer within the BOEING 220-G ecosystem.

Where earlier AFAT iterations functioned as localized aerodynamic optimization modules, X10V2 introduces a fundamental shift:

> Aerodynamics is no longer calculated — it is continuously *negotiated* across the airframe.

The aircraft becomes a **real-time aerodynamic intelligence field**, where airflow behavior, structural response, propulsion modulation, and environmental conditions are fused into a single adaptive control system.

